  <brief_title>Combined Vitrectomy and Triamcinolone in Macular Edema Secondary to Branch Retinal Vein Occlusion (BRVO)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Study Comparing Combined Vitrectomy and Triamcinolone to Laser Grid in Patients With Macular Edema Secondary to Branch Retinal Vein Occlusion (BRVO)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
